 ETG progenitors with $m_* >\n10^{10}\\mathrm{M}_\\odot$. This implies that current and future high redshift\nobservations mainly probe the birth of present-day ETGs. The source code and\ndocumentation of EMERGE are available at github.com/bmoster/emerge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2019 18:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-14"}
